sic" class="sf-depth-2">Marvin Duchow Music Library</a></li><li id="menu-806-1" class="middle odd sf-item-9 sf-depth-2 sf-no-children"><a href="/library/branches/law" class="sf-depth-2">Nahum Gelber Law Library</a></li><li id="menu-950-1" class="middle even sf-item-10 sf-depth-2 sf-no-children"><a href="/library/branches/osler" class="sf-depth-2">Osler Library of the History of Medicine</a></li><li id="menu-791-1" class="middle odd sf-item-11 sf-depth-2 sf-no-children"><a href="/library/branches/schulich" class="sf-depth-2">Schulich Library of Science &amp; Engineering</a></li><li id="menu-967-1" class="middle even sf-item-12 sf-depth-2 sf-no-children"><a href="/library/branches/rarebooks" class="sf-depth-2">Rare Books &amp; Special Collections</a></li><li id="menu-2455-1" class="middle odd sf-item-13 sf-depth-2 sf-no-children"><a href="/library/branches/research-commons" class="sf-depth-2">Research Commons</a></li><li id="menu-1847-1" class="middle even sf-item-14 sf-depth-2 sf-no-children"><a href="/library/branches/mua" class="sf-depth-2">McGill University Archives</a></li><li id="menu-955-1" class="last odd sf-item-15 sf-depth-2 sf-no-children"><a href="/library/branches/affiliated" class="sf-depth-2">Affiliated collections &amp; partner libraries</a></li></ol></li></ul></li><li id="menu-694-1" class="middle odd sf-item-5 sf-depth-1 sf-total-children-13 sf-parent-children-0 sf-single-children-13 menuparent"><a href="/library/about" class="sf-depth-1 menuparent">About</a><ul class="sf-megamenu"><li class="sf-megamenu-wrapper middle odd sf-item-5 sf-depth-1 sf-total-children-13 sf-parent-children-0 sf-single-children-13 menuparent"><ol><li id="menu-697-1" class="first odd sf-item-1 sf-depth-2 sf-no-children"><a href="/library/about/news" class="sf-depth-2">News &amp; events</a></li><li id="menu-2466-1" class="middle even sf-item-2 sf-depth-2 sf-no-children"><a href="/library/about/fiat-lux" class="sf-depth-2">Fiat Lux: Reimagining the McGill Library</a></li><li id